15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1-124, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 1-124. A. Unless otherwise specifically defined, "per-
19 pupil expenditure" shall mean the aggregate current expenditures of
20 school districts, from all funding sources including federal funds,
21 state funds and local funds, plus the direct support aggregate
22 current expenditures of the state for the day-to-day operations of
23 schools and school districts from all funding sources including
24 federal funds, divided by the aggregate student membership number
