1 C. The provisions of subsection A of this section shall apply
2 when related to the expenditure of public funds by educational and
3 governmental entities. When reporting or publishing the per-pupil
4 expenditure for any purpose, the State Department of Education shall
5 also report or publish each category of expenditure as listed in
6 subsection A of this section as well as the aggregate expenditure.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2025.
